---
import '../styles/global.css'
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en" data-theme="dark">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="Sentori pricing. Self-hosted is free forever. Hosted: free tier at 100k events/month, Pro at ¥4,900/month for 5M events and 90-day retention."
    />
    <link rel="canonical" href="https://sentori.golia.jp/pricing/" />
    <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
    <meta property="og:site_name" content="Sentori" />
    <meta property="og:title" content="Pricing — Sentori" />
    <meta property="og:description" content="Self-hosted is free forever. Hosted free tier at 100k events/month; Pro at ¥4,900/month." />
    <meta property="og:url" content="https://sentori.golia.jp/pricing/" />
    <meta property="og:image" content="https://sentori.golia.jp/og.png" />
    <meta property="og:image:width" content="1200" />
    <meta property="og:image:height" content="630" />
    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
    <meta name="twitter:title" content="Pricing — Sentori" />
    <meta name="twitter:description" content="Self-hosted is free forever. Hosted free tier at 100k events/month; Pro at ¥4,900/month." />
    <meta name="twitter:image" content="https://sentori.golia.jp/og.png" />
    <title>Pricing — Sentori</title>
  </head>
  <body class="bg-bg text-fg min-h-screen">
    <header class="border-border border-b">
      <nav class="mx-auto flex max-w-5xl items-center justify-between px-6 py-4 text-sm">
        <a href="/" class="text-fg font-semibold">Sentori</a>
        <div class="text-fg-muted flex gap-6">
          <a href="/docs" class="hover:text-fg transition-colors">Docs</a>
          <a href="/pricing" class="text-fg">Pricing</a>
          <a href="https://github.com/goliajp/sentori" class="hover:text-fg transition-colors">GitHub</a>
          <a href="/login" class="hover:text-fg transition-colors">Sign in</a>
          <a
            href="/register"
            class="bg-accent text-bg rounded-md px-3 py-1.5 font-medium transition-opacity hover:opacity-90"
          >Get started</a>
        </div>
      </nav>
    </header>

    <main class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 pt-16 pb-24">
      <h1 class="text-fg text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Pricing</h1>
      <p class="text-fg-muted mt-4 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
        Run it yourself for nothing, or let us run it. The hosted tiers
        differ only in how much they hold and for how long — same
        dashboard, same SDKs, same alerts.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-16 grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="border-border bg-bg-tertiary/30 rounded-lg border p-8">
          <div class="text-fg-muted text-xs tracking-wider uppercase">
            Self-hosted
          </div>
          <div class="text-fg mt-2 text-3xl font-semibold">Free forever</div>
          <p class="text-fg-muted mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            One <code class="text-fg font-mono">docker compose up</code> on
            any single VM. Bring your own Postgres password. No event
            limit, no retention cap, no recipient cap. Source MIT-style.
          </p>
          <ul class="text-fg-muted mt-6 space-y-2 text-sm">
            <li>• Unlimited events</li>
            <li>• Unlimited team members</li>
            <li>• Source maps + symbolication</li>
            <li>• Email alerts</li>
            <li>• Run on a $5/mo VM</li>
          </ul>
          <a
            href="/docs/self-hosting"
            class="border-border text-fg hover:bg-bg-tertiary mt-8 inline-block rounded-md border px-4 py-2 text-sm transition-colors"
          >
            Self-hosting guide →
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="border-border bg-bg-tertiary/30 rounded-lg border p-8">
          <div class="text-fg-muted text-xs tracking-wider uppercase">
            Hosted — Free
          </div>
          <div class="text-fg mt-2 text-3xl font-semibold">Free</div>
          <p class="text-fg-muted mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Hosted at <span class="text-fg font-mono">sentori.golia.jp</span>.
            Enough to instrument a real app and see whether it earns a
            place in your stack. No card required.
          </p>
          <ul class="text-fg-muted mt-6 space-y-2 text-sm">
            <li>• 100,000 events / month</li>
            <li>• 1,000,000 spans / month</li>
            <li>• 1,000 session replays / month</li>
            <li>• 30-day retention</li>
            <li>• Email alerts on new issues + quota</li>
          </ul>
          <a
            href="/register"
            class="border-border text-fg hover:bg-bg-tertiary mt-8 inline-block rounded-md border px-4 py-2 text-sm transition-colors"
          >
            Sign up — free →
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="border-accent/40 bg-accent/5 rounded-lg border p-8">
          <div class="text-fg-muted text-xs tracking-wider uppercase">
            Hosted — Pro
          </div>
          <div class="text-fg mt-2 text-3xl font-semibold">
            ¥4,900<span class="text-fg-muted text-base font-normal"> / month</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-fg-muted mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Fifty times the volume and three times the history. Billed in
            JPY; if you are elsewhere your bank converts at the rate on
            the day, and checkout shows you an estimate first.
          </p>
          <ul class="text-fg-muted mt-6 space-y-2 text-sm">
            <li>• 5,000,000 events / month</li>
            <li>• 50,000,000 spans / month</li>
            <li>• 50,000 session replays / month</li>
            <li>• 90-day retention</li>
            <li>• Everything in Free</li>
          </ul>
          <a
            href="/register"
            class="bg-accent text-bg mt-8 inline-block rounded-md px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium transition-opacity hover:opacity-90"
          >
            Start free, upgrade later →
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="border-border mt-12 rounded-lg border p-6">
        <div class="text-fg-muted text-xs tracking-wider uppercase">
          Enterprise
        </div>
        <p class="text-fg-muted mt-3 max-w-2xl text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Unmetered volume and 365-day retention, on a contract rather
          than a card. If you need a signed agreement, an invoice, or
          limits nobody has written down yet,
          mail <a class="text-fg hover:text-accent font-mono" href="mailto:takagi@golia.jp">takagi@golia.jp</a>.
        </p>
      </div>

      <p class="text-fg-muted mt-12 max-w-2xl text-xs leading-relaxed">
        Self-hosted will always be free. The hosted tiers exist so we can
        offer a zero-ops option; revenue from Pro funds development that
        also benefits the open-source build. Upgrading and cancelling are
        both self-serve — a cancelled workspace falls back to Free limits
        and keeps its data for the Free retention window.
      </p>
    </main>

    <footer class="border-border border-t">
      <div class="text-fg-muted mx-auto flex max-w-5xl items-center justify-between px-6 py-8 text-xs">
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <a class="hover:text-fg" href="/legal/privacy">Privacy</a>
          <a class="hover:text-fg" href="/legal/terms">Terms</a>
        </div>
        <span>Built in Tokyo.</span>
      </div>
    </footer>
    <script>
      import { initSentori } from '@goliapkg/sentori-javascript'
      const token = import.meta.env.PUBLIC_SENTORI_TOKEN
      if (token) {
        initSentori({
          token,
          ingestUrl: 'https://ingest.sentori.golia.jp',
          release: `marketing@${import.meta.env.PUBLIC_GIT_SHA ?? '0.0.0'}`,
          environment: 'prod',
        })
      }
    </script>
  </body>
</html>
